			<div class="content" id="post-content-4391722">
									

<p>Hey, this is just me spitballing here for a probable base for MTF Alpha-Niner Last Hope.<br />
I haven't done much reading with the Omega 7 story arc, but I have read the whole of Resurrection story list.</p>
<p>Heli-carrier. Again, this is not some Marvel fanboy input, the problem I see with the MTF Last hope is tied to the saying, &quot;Putting All your Eggs in one Basket.&quot; If they set up shop at any of the sites, they risk the problem of putting the site as a target by the other relevant organizations, such as what happen with Girls Night Out.</p>
<p>This brings me back to the Heli-carrier but again. If it is large enough, (And I'm basing this on the scale the Heli-carrier in the MCU in Avengers) and more overall design right you can essentially have a mobile containment site. They can of course be temporary for when the item recovered during a raid or something similar like the the SCP-008 outbreak that 105 help sort out. Or even keep 'useful' SCP on the Heli-carrier for the MTF to use in particular situation.</p>
<p>Again, you will end up 'putting all your eggs in one basket' but at least it mobile. You can even call the ship 'The Sword of Damocles' to reflect the important of what the Heli-carrier and its mission objective.</p>

